## Patrick Chan, Canadian Figure Skater 
Patrick Chan is a former competitive figure skater. He is a three-time World Champion and a two time Olympic Medalist. 
He participated in the Olympics three times, in 2010, 2014, and 2018. 

Patrick retired after the 2018 Pyeongchang Olympics. He is currently residing in Vancouver and enjoying retirement. 

The former skater also produces his own line of ice wine partnered with Flat Rock Cellars at Niagara Falls. 
Fun fact: He once got kicked out of Liquor Barn for not having his ID. 
> So the lady told him he was going to have to leave the store. LEAVE THE STORE! They kicked Patrick Chan out of the Liquor Barn. 

